Chairs are placed at a "roadside patio" in North Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, June 14, 2020. Municipal governments in Metro Vancouver are repurposing roads in the region by reducing vehicle lanes to open "roadside patios", which provides pedestrians with more safe spaces to move around and practice physical distancing, as well as to help support businesses during the dire economic challenges. (Photo by Liang Sen/Xinhua) 

